second-rank tensors with natural zero boundary 
conditions at
infinity
     
In what follows we will not specify the tensor 
structure of the
Green's functions of  implicitly assuming that it 
is always
determined by the nature of the quantity acted upon by 
.

The term  in (
)
reflects the gauge ambiguity in the solution of (
